======================================================================
POSITION MIXING ANALYSIS
======================================================================

For interior v: the relative 2-cycle ALWAYS has terms at all 3 positions.
For source v: only pos-0 terms.
For sink v: only pos-2 terms.

The delta image for interior v comes from mixing all three positions,
creating a 1-chain that cannot be a boundary in T\v.

Let's verify this algebraic mechanism:

